  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to determine whether the addition of systematic pelvic
      lymphadenectomy to hysterectomy with bilateral adnexectomy improves disease-free survival
      (DFS) and overall survival (OS) in patients with preoperatively supposed Stage I-II
      endometrial cancer
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
